{
  "name": "polymath",
  "description": "Polymath-only catalog metadata kept out of .claude-plugin/marketplace.json so the marketplace manifest passes `claude plugin validate --strict`. Read by tools/conformance.sh (MANIFEST-3 status gate), tools/build-catalog.py (HTML status badges), and tools/sync-connector-policy.py (connector-policy README disclosure block).",
