    "notes": "Polymath declares conformance with the agentskills.io v1.0 open standard for SKILL.md format. All skills under this marketplace use the SKILL.md shape: frontmatter (name + description \u2264 200 chars) + body procedure. Skills are portable across any harness that implements the standard."
